data.description: Don't miss this adorable ranch on almost 11 acres! This very private and level property sits on a creek, features a classic barn, large two bay shop, fenced garden area, and pastures for all your animals! Inside the home you'll find an open concept kitchen, living room, and large family room. New roof in 2020. Don't miss this one!
